high_descs: Turn through the kitchen and get to the fridge in the corner.
Remove the butterknife from the fridge.
Turn and go back to where you started, at the other end of the kitchen next to the potato counters.
Slice the potato in the box and shut the box.
Turn to the countertop on the right.
Place the butterknife down on the countertop.
Go back to the potato box.
Remove a potato slice from the box.
Move around the counters and go to the sink on the end of the sink.
Place the potato slice into the sink, rinse the potato with water and pick it back up.
Go back to the countertop where the knife was placed.
Place the potato slice next to the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of Potato, rinse the slice in water, and place it on a CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the butterknife from the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around to walk to the end of the counter to reach the potato on the left of the kitchen.
Slice the potato in the box with the knife and close the box.
Turn left to head to the kitchen countertop.
Put the butterknife on the countertop.
Move to the left to face the potato and open it.
Pick up a slice of potato from the box.
Turn around to walk to the larger sink at the end of the counter.
Wash the potato and pick it out.
Walk left to reach the end of the countertop and turn right to face the countertop.
Place the potato next to the knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Place the washed potato on the countertop.

high_descs: walk around the countertop to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator and grab a potato with a butterknife.
walk to the other side of the kitchen where a potato is on the floor.
Put the potato inside the box and then close the box.
walk over to the countertop and put the stick-on top of the countertop.
open the box and take out the butterknife that is on the countertop.
walk over to where the potato is.
Turn the potato on and put the sponge under it.
Take the sponge out of the sink.
go around to the other side and look for a place to put the potato.
sit on the barstool that is in front of the countertop.
Put the potato on top of the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Getting a potato and washing it on the countertop.
